Revision history for perl module File::TTX

0.01 2010-07-09

 - Initial release

0.02 2010-07-14

 - Corrected the required version of XML::xmlapi in Makefile.PL

0.03 2011-03-12
        
 - Added append_copy, source_xml and translated_xml to permit easy filter writing.
 - Added 'from'=>TTX option for creating new TTXs with the headers of an old one.
 - Added ->copy_headers to do that actual work.

0.04 2014-05-12

 - Moved off of xmlapi to XML::Snap
 - Added some functionality last year - still a ways to go, now that TTX is nearly obsolete
